{"tid":2053083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【一週年】一班羊仔爲咗抵抗大灰狼，守護羊村嘅故事","createTime":"2020-06-06T04:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T08:21:59.000Z","uid":221035,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8faa885dc8048a252802caf8aea9d6bfd41ba471","tid":2053083,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCPQmPG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCPQmPG.png&h=b6f0c121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XqLU9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XqLU9H.png&h=8dba371b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5deQmPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5deQmPH.png&h=6cee28c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7iEZBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7iEZBo.png&h=ad501179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔cap曬出嚟，呢個其實係手足做嘅兒童繪本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲公仔好得意啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文：香港言語治療師總工會<br />\n圖：rainection<br />\n親子共讀：4-7歲<br />\n自己閱讀：7歲以上<br />\n<br />\n內容撮要：<br />\n羊咩咩一直喺羊村落入面過住安穩又平淡嘅生活。<br />\n有一日，牧羊人突然離開，隔離嘅狼村落派咗大灰狼去帶領佢哋。<br />\n從此佢哋嘅生活變得唔再一樣：講嘅語言唔同咗、睇嘅書唔同咗、生活習慣唔同咗，生活變得唔再自由。<br />\n過咗一段時間，大灰狼宣佈要實施「狼羊規矩」：狼村落入面嘅狼可以隨意去到羊村落嗰度食羊。<br />\n羊咩咩們眼見自己嘅屋企將要消失，佢哋又會點做呢？<br />\n<br />\n電子版可以喺呢度睇到：<a href=\"https://issuu.com/guhkst/docs/_e7_be_8a_e6_9d_91_e5_ae_88_e8_a1_9b_e8_80_85_fina\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fissuu.com%2Fguhkst%2Fdocs%2F_e7_be_8a_e6_9d_91_e5_ae_88_e8_a1_9b_e8_80_85_fina&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=d7008b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://issuu.com/guhkst/docs/_e7_be_8a_e6_9d_91_e5_ae_88_e8_a1_9b_e8_80_85_fina</a><br />\n<br />\n實體版喺以下黃店有得攞啦! <br />\n銅鑼灣：Peek-a-Poke <br />\n旺角：傲瞳視力眼鏡店, Hair guys salon, 阿木台灣麵, 大勝丼<br />\n屯門：東屋台"},{"pid":"c6a31378d5c7fee3b10a51f959b3389ac5581b93","tid":2053083,"uid":221035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"咁多位羊仔，唔好放棄啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8d1ca3a777c3b4489f100fea2719895b2e196e","tid":2053083,"uid":67339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d249543f798f8d0abd79bcd7a97bc4ee190cde38","tid":2053083,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965fbfbe73b62ba9899257efa6868fb71a8c76a0","tid":2053083,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067c4b19624d31b3341116adf98b13cbb47baec1","tid":2053083,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"504a8afa5e5d9b851671a5a8d01b588f7cb1a9c5","tid":2053083,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"abb584be6b7545d08bca71f890cd856c97fad473","tid":2053083,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"唔好嘥咗手足一番心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76123760884a9f7bcacf893abdfef7a43aeb15fb","tid":2053083,"uid":335303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有用，推</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8vDYvJU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8vDYvJU.gif&h=23492281&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"927a145a1ab